Title: Wei22_full
Description: Single-cell Stereo-seq spatial transcriptomics data with serial sections along the rostral-caudal axis of axolotl brain tissues, collected at 2 (3 sections), 5 (3 sections), 10 (3 sections),  15 (4 sections) and 20 (3 sections) days post injury (DPI) after removal of a portion of the dorsal pallium of the 11 cm length axolotl. Represented as a SpatialExperiment; derived from https://db.cngb.org/stomics/artista/download/.

Title: Wei22_example
Description: A subset of the Wei22_full dataset, focusing on fewer regeneration stages. It includes 2 (2 sections), 10 (2 sections),  and 20 (2 sections) days post injury (DPI).
